# Conversation Distillation Trigger

When the following signals appear, read `.cursor/skills/memory-bank/SKILL.md` **Part 2** and execute distillation:

- User says "done", "that's it", "wrapping up", "end of day"
- A complete analysis task finished (report published)
- Solved a specific technical/business problem
- Hit a gotcha and found the solution
- Made a decision with trade-offs

Don't distill: Q&A, casual chat, trivial one-liner operations.

Quick harvest command (see Skill for details):

```shell
npx tsx src/harvest.ts add --category "finding" --title "Title" --content "Content" --tags "tags"
```
